  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT276-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tōḻikkuk kuṟaimaṟāmal talaimakaṉ kūṟiyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">HE speaking to the confidante, that [she] may not refuse
          [his] request. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT276">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> paṇaittōṭ kuṟumakaḷ pāvai taiiyum</l>
          <l> pañcāyp paḷḷañ cūḻntu maṟṟiva</l>
          <l> ḷurutteḻu vaṉamulai yoḷipeṟa veḻutiya</l>
          <l> toyyil kāppō raṟitalu maṟiyār</l>
          <l> muṟaiyuṭai yaracaṉ ceṅkō lavaiyat</l>
          <l> tiyāṉṟaṟ kaṭaviṉ yāṅkā vatukol</l>
          <l> peritum pētai maṉṟa</l>
          <l> vaḷitō tāṉēyiv vaḻuṅka lūrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Those who keep watch [on her] have no idea of the sandal paste,</l>
          <l rend="indent">which, to obtain brightness,</l>
          <l rend="indent6">she has drawn on [her] shapely rising pretty breasts,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">nor also just that the ditch is surrounded by Pañcāy grass </l>
          <l rend="indent2">nor also that an image of the small woman with bamboo</l>
          <l rend="indent9">shoulders has been fashioned .</l>
          <l>If I urged </l>
          <l rend="indent2">in the assembly under the impartial staff of a just king ,</l>
          <l rend="indent6">what would happen?</l>
          <l>And great [is] folly indeed.</l>
          <l>Ah, it seems pitiful, this noisy village.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
